torrentkino (0.10) wheezy; urgency=low

  * Renamed masala to torrentkino.
  * Merged tumbleweed into torrentkino.
  * Switched to Linus Torvalds SHA1 implementation.
  * AES support is off by default. Needs PolarSSL. See Makefile.
  * ARM support. Tested on Raspbian/Raspberry PI.
  * Ignore link-local polution.
  * Use info_hash database for lookups too for 2 node only swarms.
  * Better startup timings for 2 node only swarms.

